1. Otišli smo u *restoran* sinoć. (We went to a restaurant last night.)
2. Konobar nam je preporučio ovaj *restoran*. (The waiter recommended this restaurant to us.)
3. Naš *restoran* nudi specijalitete iz različitih krajeva sveta. (Our restaurant offers specialties from different parts of the world.)
4. *Restoran* je bio prepun kada smo stigli. (The restaurant was crowded when we arrived.)
5. Pogledajte meni našeg *restorana*. (Take a look at our restaurant's menu.)
6. Radnici su renovirali *restoran* pre otvaranja. (The workers renovated the restaurant before opening.)
7. Naša firma organizuje *restoranske* događaje za različite prilike. (Our company organizes restaurant events for various occasions.)
8. Konobari u ovom *restoranu* su uvek ljubazni prema gostima. (The waiters in this restaurant are always polite to guests.)
9. Tražim posao u *restoranu*. (I'm looking for a job in a restaurant.)
10. Želimo da rezervišemo sto u ovom *restoranu*. (We want to book a table in this restaurant.)